{"tid":835431,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】李嘉欣騷腿孖老公福臨門做節 Jayden禮貌回應記者祝福","createTime":"2018-09-25T01:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T14:41:21.000Z","uid":48905,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d3657e07c5e8cb4ad0a616a8a015124a6328e2bd","tid":835431,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"今晚係農曆八月十五中秋節，好多人都會約埋屋企人食飯慶祝，好似許晉亨同李嘉欣夫婦咁，今年都唔例外，喺今晚6點40分左右，佢哋一家三口坐七人車到達灣仔福臨門食飯做節。<br />\n<br />\n坐喺車頭嘅許晉亨率先落車，之後去後座扶妻兒落車，李嘉欣今年着連身裙現身，騷腿好搶眼吓，之後到佢哋個仔許建彤（Jayden）到車，已經7歲大嘅Jayden今日着住西裝，戴住副眼鏡現身。當記者上身向許氏一家三口送上祝福時，Jayden好有禮貌同家教，回番記者：「我真係恭喜你呀！」<br />\n<br />\n到李嘉欣行入酒樓等電梯時，佢似乎刻意俾囝囝企喺佢哋兩公婆前面，入電梯後又俾個仔企入邊，似乎想減低囝囝嘅曝光機會。<br />\n<br />\n而許晉亨嘅堂兄許晉奎就喺接近晚上7點到達福臨門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/095422_b241e020c7317dea5085eb7ff75eafc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F095422_b241e020c7317dea5085eb7ff75eafc9.png&h=956ab9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 李嘉欣騷腿</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/095455_abd075f02aac43a224a1cd7b2414876f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F095455_abd075f02aac43a224a1cd7b2414876f.png&h=28536a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 不過佢哋一直都好好笑容，態度友善。(蘋果日報)</span>"},{"pid":"7939dd17c291192a978622544dd1d45e97a90cef","tid":835431,"uid":21918,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"佢扮牙朗射罰球呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d043eabd8307ac9bea9a73d11f55e740c7831c","tid":835431,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"唔知佢地成班圍埋食飯會傾d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f3ce19fa8fd3fc37c143b0667202a762b9dfd7","tid"